<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome User</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #FF4B2B;
      --secondary: #FF416C;
      --light-bg: #f6f5f7;
      --input-bg: #eee;
      --text-dark: #333;
      --text-error: red;
      --border-light: #DDDDDD;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--light-bg);
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .circle {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      opacity: 0.15;
      animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
    }

    .circle.one {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      top: 10%;
      left: 10%;
    }

    .circle.two {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      bottom: 10%;
      right: 15%;
      animation-delay: 3s;
    }

    @keyframes rotate {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
      50% { transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.1); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1); }
    }

    .welcome-container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    .welcome-container h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .welcome-container p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--primary);
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }

    .quote {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: slideIn 1s ease-in-out 1.5s forwards;
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .logout-btn {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      animation: zoomIn 1s ease-in-out 2s forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .logout-btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--secondary);
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    @keyframes zoomIn {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.9);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="circle one"></div>
  <div class="circle two"></div>

  <div class="welcome-container">
    <div class="avatar">A</div>
    <h1>Welcome, Amruth üëã</h1>
    <p>‚ÄúStay focused and never stop learning.‚Äù</p>
    <div class="quote">Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out.</div>
    <button class="logout-btn" onclick="logout()">Logout</button>
  </div>

  <script>
    function logout() {
      alert("You‚Äôve been logged out. See you again!");
     
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
